'''失落的世界'''（{{lang-en|''Lost Worlds''}}）是一个[[歷史頻道|歷史頻道]]纪录片电视系列节目，探讨了从古代到现代的各种各样“失落”的事物，并这些“伟大的壮举”背后的工程、技术和文化<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.history.com/content/lostworlds/about-the-series|title=About the Series|accessdate=12 June 2012|work=history.com|publisher=The History Channel|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100209172830/http://www.history.com/content/lostworlds/about-the-series|archivedate=2010-02-09|quote=A team of field investigators and engineering experts went out into the world in search of clues about these great feats of engineering, technology, and culture in order to bring them back to life with modern-day graphic technology.|dead-url=no}}</ref>，使用考古证据与在有关专家的采访，并通过[[電腦成像|CGI]]重建当时的情景<ref name="about-vid">{{Cite web|url=http://www.history.com/videos/lost-worlds-about-lost-worlds#lost-worlds-about-lost-worlds|title=About Lost Worlds|accessdate=12 June 2012|format=video|work=history.com|publisher=The History Channel}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

